{"thig14.1:0.1":"Therigatha 14.1 ","thig14.1:0.2":"Timsanipata ","thig14.1:0.3":"Subhajivakambavanikatherigatha ","thig14.1:1.1":"Jivakambavanam rammam, ","thig14.1:1.2":"Gacchantim bhikkhunim subham; ","thig14.1:1.3":"Dhuttako sannivaresi, ","thig14.1:1.4":"Tamenam abravi subha. ","thig14.1:2.1":"“Kim te aparadhitam maya, ","thig14.1:2.2":"Yam mam ovariyana titthasi; ","thig14.1:2.3":"Na hi pabbajitaya avuso, ","thig14.1:2.4":"Puriso samphusanaya kappati. ","thig14.1:3.1":"Garuke mama satthusasane, ","thig14.1:3.2":"Ya sikkha sugatena desita; ","thig14.1:3.3":"Parisuddhapadam ananganam, ","thig14.1:3.4":"Kim mam ovariyana titthasi. ","thig14.1:4.1":"Avilacitto anavilam, ","thig14.1:4.2":"Sarajo vitarajam ananganam; ","thig14.1:4.3":"Sabbattha vimuttamanasam, ","thig14.1:4.4":"Kim mam ovariyana titthasi”. ","thig14.1:5.1":"“Dahara ca apapika casi, ","thig14.1:5.2":"Kim te pabbajja karissati; ","thig14.1:5.3":"Nikkhipa kasayacivaram, ","thig14.1:5.4":"Ehi ramama supupphite vane. ","thig14.1:6.1":"Madhuranca pavanti sabbaso, ","thig14.1:6.2":"Kusumarajena samutthita duma; ","thig14.1:6.3":"Pathamavasanto sukho utu, ","thig14.1:6.4":"Ehi ramama supupphite vane. ","thig14.1:7.1":"Kusumitasikhara ca padapa, ","thig14.1:7.2":"Abhigajjantiva maluterita; ","thig14.1:7.3":"Ka tuyham rati bhavissati, ","thig14.1:7.4":"Yadi eka vanamogahissasi. ","thig14.1:8.1":"Valamigasanghasevitam, ","thig14.1:8.2":"Kunjaramattakarenulolitam; ","thig14.1:8.3":"Asahayika gantumicchasi, ","thig14.1:8.4":"Rahitam bhimsanakam mahavanam. ","thig14.1:9.1":"Tapaniyakatava dhitika, ","thig14.1:9.2":"Vicarasi cittalateva acchara; ","thig14.1:9.3":"Kasikasukhumehi vaggubhi, ","thig14.1:9.4":"Sobhasi suvasanehi nupame. ","thig14.1:10.1":"Aham tava vasanugo siyam, ","thig14.1:10.2":"Yadi viharemase kananantare; ","thig14.1:10.3":"Na hi matthi taya piyattaro, ","thig14.1:10.4":"Pano kinnarimandalocane. ","thig14.1:11.1":"Yadi me vacanam karissasi, ","thig14.1:11.2":"Sukhita ehi agaramavasa; ","thig14.1:11.3":"Pasadanivatavasini, ","thig14.1:11.4":"Parikammam te karontu nariyo. ","thig14.1:12.1":"Kasikasukhumani dharaya, ","thig14.1:12.2":"Abhiropehi ca malavannakam; ","thig14.1:12.3":"Kancanamanimuttakam bahum, ","thig14.1:12.4":"Vividham abharanam karomi te. ","thig14.1:13.1":"Sudhotarajapacchadam subham, ","thig14.1:13.2":"Gonakatulikasanthatam navam; ","thig14.1:13.3":"Abhiruha sayanam maharaham, ","thig14.1:13.4":"Candanamanditasaragandhikam. ","thig14.1:14.1":"Uppalam cudaka samuggatam, ","thig14.1:14.2":"Yatha tam amanussasevitam; ","thig14.1:14.3":"Evam tvam brahmacarini, ","thig14.1:14.4":"Sakesangesu jaram gamissasi”. ","thig14.1:15.1":"“Kim te idha sarasammatam, ","thig14.1:15.2":"Kunapapuramhi susanavaddhane; ","thig14.1:15.3":"Bhedanadhamme kalevare, ","thig14.1:15.4":"Yam disva vimano udikkhasi”. ","thig14.1:16.1":"“Akkhini ca turiyariva, ","thig14.1:16.2":"Kinnariyariva pabbatantare; ","thig14.1:16.3":"Tava me nayanani dakkhiya, ","thig14.1:16.4":"Bhiyyo kamarati pavaddhati. ","thig14.1:17.1":"Uppalasikharopamani te, ","thig14.1:17.2":"Vimale hatakasannibhe mukhe; ","thig14.1:17.3":"Tava me nayanani dakkhiya, ","thig14.1:17.4":"Bhiyyo kamaguno pavaddhati. ","thig14.1:18.1":"Api duragata saramhase, ","thig14.1:18.2":"Ayatapamhe visuddhadassane; ","thig14.1:18.3":"Na hi matthi taya piyattaro, ","thig14.1:18.4":"Nayana kinnarimandalocane”. ","thig14.1:19.1":"“Apathena payatumicchasi, ","thig14.1:19.2":"Candam kilanakam gavesasi; ","thig14.1:19.3":"Merum langhetumicchasi, ","thig14.1:19.4":"Yo tvam buddhasutam maggayasi. ","thig14.1:20.1":"Natthi hi loke sadevake, ","thig14.1:20.2":"Rago yatthapi dani me siya; ","thig14.1:20.3":"Napi nam janami kiriso, ","thig14.1:20.4":"Atha maggena hato samulako. ","thig14.1:21.1":"Ingalakuyava ujjhito, ","thig14.1:21.2":"Visapattoriva aggito kato; ","thig14.1:21.3":"Napi nam passami kiriso, ","thig14.1:21.4":"Atha maggena hato samulako. ","thig14.1:22.1":"Yassa siya apaccavekkhitam, ","thig14.1:22.2":"Sattha va anupasito siya; ","thig14.1:22.3":"Tvam tadisikam palobhaya, ","thig14.1:22.4":"Janantim so imam vihannasi. ","thig14.1:23.1":"Mayhanhi akkutthavandite, ","thig14.1:23.2":"Sukhadukkhe ca sati upatthita; ","thig14.1:23.3":"Sankhatamasubhanti janiya, ","thig14.1:23.4":"Sabbattheva mano na limpati. ","thig14.1:24.1":"Saham sugatassa savika, ","thig14.1:24.2":"Maggatthangikayanayayini; ","thig14.1:24.3":"Uddhatasalla anasava, ","thig14.1:24.4":"Sunnagaragata ramamaham. ","thig14.1:25.1":"Dittha hi maya sucittita, ","thig14.1:25.2":"Sombha darukapillakani va; ","thig14.1:25.3":"Tantihi ca khilakehi ca, ","thig14.1:25.4":"Vinibaddha vividham panaccaka. ","thig14.1:26.1":"Tamhuddhate tantikhilake, ","thig14.1:26.2":"Vissatthe vikale parikrite; ","thig14.1:26.3":"Na vindeyya khandaso kate, ","thig14.1:26.4":"Kimhi tattha manam nivesaye. ","thig14.1:27.1":"Tathupama dehakani mam, ","thig14.1:27.2":"Tehi dhammehi vina na vattanti; ","thig14.1:27.3":"Dhammehi vina na vattati, ","thig14.1:27.4":"Kimhi tattha manam nivesaye. ","thig14.1:28.1":"Yatha haritalena makkhitam, ","thig14.1:28.2":"Addasa cittikam bhittiya katam; ","thig14.1:28.3":"Tamhi te viparitadassanam, ","thig14.1:28.4":"Sanna manusika niratthika. ","thig14.1:29.1":"Mayam viya aggato katam, ","thig14.1:29.2":"Supinanteva suvannapadapam; ","thig14.1:29.3":"Upagacchasi andha rittakam, ","thig14.1:29.4":"Janamajjheriva rupparupakam. ","thig14.1:30.1":"Vattaniriva kotarohita, ","thig14.1:30.2":"Majjhe pubbulaka saassuka; ","thig14.1:30.3":"Pilakolika cettha jayati, ","thig14.1:30.4":"Vividha cakkhuvidha ca pindita”. ","thig14.1:31.1":"Uppatiya carudassana, ","thig14.1:31.2":"Na ca pajjittha asangamanasa; ","thig14.1:31.3":"“Handa te cakkhum harassu tam”, ","thig14.1:31.4":"Tassa narassa adasi tavade. ","thig14.1:32.1":"Tassa ca viramasi tavade, ","thig14.1:32.2":"Rago tattha khamapayi ca nam; ","thig14.1:32.3":"“Sotthi siya brahmacarini, ","thig14.1:32.4":"Na puno edisakam bhavissati”. ","thig14.1:33.1":"“Asadiya edisam janam, ","thig14.1:33.2":"Aggim pajjalitamva lingiya; ","thig14.1:33.3":"Ganhiya asivisam viya, ","thig14.1:33.4":"Api nu sotthi siya khamehi no”. ","thig14.1:34.1":"Mutta ca tato sa bhikkhuni, ","thig14.1:34.2":"Agami buddhavarassa santikam; ","thig14.1:34.3":"Passiya varapunnalakkhanam, ","thig14.1:34.4":"Cakkhu asi yatha puranakanti. ","thig14.1:35.1":"… Subha jivakambavanika theri …. ","thig14.1:36.1":"Timsanipato nitthito. "}